After 7 Tauri apps, I type the same commands constantly. Here's the reference I wish existed when I started.
# New project
npm create tauri-app@latest

# Add to existing project
npm install --save-dev @tauri-apps/cli
npx tauri init

# Dev mode (hot reload)
